metadata.name: God save king girl
metadata.description:
"Dad, today is the kindergarten art performance, can you come to see the sweet performance?"



"They said She had no father and was a wild child, and they beat me."



In the first mental hospital of Zhonghai City, Yang Yi received a strange phone call.



"Little sister, have you got the wrong number?"



"Aren't you father? Sweet is such a wild kid, huh? But my mother said I have a father, my father's name is Yang Yi, he is the best father in the world, but my father is on a mission in outer space, can't come back!"
